   compileSdkVersion getExtOrIntegerDefault("compileSdkVersion")
 
+  // Pin to the project's NDK instead of AGP's baked-in default. This module
+  // builds native code via CMake but ships no ndkVersion, so AGP would request
+  // its default NDK (e.g. 27.0.12077973) which isn't installed by our nix SDK
